News.Title: Medicamen Organics Enters Beauty and Personal Care Sector
News.Summary: Medicamen Organics has announced a strategic entry into the beauty and personal care sector. The company is expanding its business portfolio to include beauty and personal care products. No specific details about the products or the scale of this new venture were provided in the news snippet.

News.Title: Medicamen Organics Invests in Nepalese Manufacturing Facility
News.Summary: Medicamen Organics has made an investment in Medi Hub Organic's manufacturing facility located in Nepal, strengthening its regional presence. This move is expected to enhance the company's production capabilities and expand its market reach in the region.
